<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pave-vt">pave <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /peɪv/    美 /peɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[常用于被动语态] 铺（路、地面等）</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="pave-the-way">pave the way</h3>
<p>1.<strong>铺平道路；创造条件：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In China, many parents arrange everything for their children and <strong>pave the way for</strong> their success.
在中国，许多父母为孩子安排一切，为他们的成功铺路。</p><footer>2013福建书面表达改</footer></div></div>